        "text": "the throne of the Lord, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "because the Lord himself was, in a peculiar manner, the king and governor of Israel. He had the founding, he had the filling of their throne, by immediate direction.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
